\c 20
\s Ukuvuka kukaJesu
\p
\v 1 Kwathi ngolokuqala lweviki uMariya Magadalena wafika engcwabeni ekuseni kakhulu, kusesemnyama\x + 20.1,2, Mat. 28.1-8. Mark. 16.1-8. Luka 24.1-9.\x*, wabona ilitshe lisusiwe engcwabeni\x + Mat. 27.60. Mark. 15.46. Joha. 11.38,39,41.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho wagijima weza kuSimoni Petro lakomunye umfundi uJesu ayemthanda\x + 13.23.\x*, wathi kubo: Bayisusile iNkosi engcwabeni, njalo kasazi lapho abayibeke khona.
\v 3 Ngakho uPetro waphuma lomunye umfundi, bafika engcwabeni\x + Luka 24.12,24.\x*.
\v 4 Basebegijima bobabili kanyekanye; omunye umfundi wasegijima phambili ngesiqubu kuloPetro, wafika kuqala engcwabeni.
\v 5 Kwathi ekhothama elunguza\x + 20.11. Luka 24.12.\x* wabona amalembu acolekileyo endlelwe, kodwa kangenanga\x + 19.40.\x*.
\v 6 USimoni Petro wasefika emlandela, wangena engcwabeni, wabona amalembu acolekileyo endlelwe\x + 19.40.\x*,
\v 7 lelembu lobuso elalisekhanda lakhe, lingabekwanga lamalembu acolekileyo\x + 11.44. Luka 19.20.\x*, kodwa lendluliwe lisendaweni \add yalo\add* lodwa.
\v 8 Ngakho wasengena laye omunye umfundi owayefike kuqala engcwabeni, wabona, wakholwa;
\v 9 ngoba babengakaqedisisi\x + Mat. 22.29.\x* umbhalo, ukuthi ubemele ukuvuka kwabafileyo\x + Hlab. 16.10. Seb. 2.25-31.13.34,35. Joha. 2.22.\x*.
\v 10 Basebesuka futhi abafundi baya kubo\x + Luka 24.12.\x*.
\s Ukuzibonakalisa kukaJesu
\p
\v 11 Kodwa uMariya wema engcwabeni phandle ekhala\x + 20.1,2.\x*; kwathi esakhala, wakhothama walunguza engcwabeni\x + 20.11. Luka 24.12.\x*,
\v 12 wasebona ingilosi ezimbili \add zembethe\add* ezimhlophe zihlezi, enye ingasekhanda, lenye ingasenyaweni, lapho isidumbu sikaJesu ebesilele khona\x + Luka 24.4.\x*.
\v 13 Zona zasezisithi kuye: Mama, ukhalelani? Wathi kuzo: Ngoba bayithethe iNkosi yami, njalo kangazi lapho abayibeke khona.
\v 14 Kwathi esetshilo lezizinto watshibilika, wabona uJesu emi\x + Mark. 16.9. Mat. 28.9.\x*, kodwa wayengazi ukuthi nguJesu\x + 21.4. Luka 24.16.\x*.
\v 15 UJesu wathi kuye: Mama, ukhalelani? Udinga bani\x + 1.38.\x*? Yena ecabanga ukuthi ngumphathi wesivande, wathi kuye: Nkosi, uba wena umsusile, ngitshele lapho ombeke khona, mina-ke ngizamthatha\x + 12.6.\x*.
\v 16 UJesu wathi kuye: Mariya! Yena watshibilika wathi kuye: Raboni! okuyikuthi: Mfundisi\x + Mark. 10.51. Joha. 1.38.\x*.
\v 17 UJesu wathi kuye: Ungangibambi, ngoba kangikenyukeli kuBaba\x + Luka 24.51.\x*; kodwa yana kubafowethu\x + Mat. 28.10.\x*, uthi kubo: Ngiyenyukela kuBaba loYihlo\x + 14.12.\x*, la\add ku\add*Nkulunkulu wami loNkulunkulu wenu\x + Efe. 1.17. 1 Kor. 3.23.\x*.
\v 18 UMariya Magadalena weza wababikela abafundi ukuthi uyibonile iNkosi, njalo imtshele lezizinto\x + Mark. 16.10. Mat. 28.10. Luka 24.10,22,23.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Kwathi kusihlwa ngalolosuku, olokuqala lweviki\x + Mark. 16.14. Luka 24.36. 1 Kor. 15.5.\x*, leminyango ivaliwe lapho abafundi ababehlangene khona\x + 20.26.\x*, ngenxa yokwesaba amaJuda\x + 7.13.\x*, uJesu wafika wema phakathi\x + Luka 24.36. Luka 24.15. 21.4.\x*, wathi kubo: Ukuthula \add kakube\add* kini\x + 14.27.\x*.
\v 20 Njalo esetshilo lokhu wabatshengisa izandla \add zakhe\add* lohlangothi lwakhe\x + 20.25. Luka 24.40.\x*. Ngakho abafundi bathokoza beyibona iNkosi\x + 16.22.\x*.
\v 21 UJesu wasebuya esithi kubo: Ukuthula \add kakube\add* kini\x + 14.27.\x*; njengoba\x + 17.18. Mat. 28.18-20. 2 Tim. 2.2. Heb. 3.1.\x* uBaba engithumile, lami ngiyalithuma\x + 17.3.\x*.
\v 22 Kwathi esetshilo lokhu waphephetha phezu \add kwabo\add* wathi kubo: Yemukelani uMoya oNgcwele\x + Gen. 2.7.\x*.
\v 23 Loba ngobani elithethelela izono zabo, bathethelelwe; loba ngobani elibamba ezabo, zibanjiwe\x + Mat. 16.19.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Kodwa uTomasi, omunye wabalitshumi lambili, othiwa nguDidimusi, wayengekho labo mhla uJesu efika\x + 11.16.\x*.
\v 25 Ngakho abanye abafundi bathi kuye: Siyibonile iNkosi. Kodwa yena wathi kubo: Uba ngingaboni ezandleni zayo amanxeba ezipikili, njalo ngifake umunwe wami enxebeni lezipikili, njalo ngibeke izandla zami ehlangothini lwayo, kangisoze ngikholwe\x + 20.20. Hlab. 22.16.\x*.
\v 26 Njalo emva kwensuku eziyisificaminwembili abafundi bakhe babephakathi futhi, loTomasi elabo. UJesu wafika\x + Mark. 16.14.\x*, iminyango ivaliwe, wema phakathi wathi\x + 20.19.\x*: Ukuthula \add kakube\add* kini\x + 14.27.\x*.
\v 27 Wasesithi kuTomasi: Letha umunwe wakho lapha, ubone izandla zami; njalo letha isandla sakho, u\add si\add*fake ehlangothini lwami; njalo ungabi ngongakholwayo, kodwa okholwayo\x + Luka 24.39. 1 Joha. 1.1.\x*.
\v 28 UTomasi wasephendula, wathi kuye: Nkosi yami loNkulunkulu wami!
\v 29 UJesu wathi kuye: Ngoba usungibonile, Tomasi, ukholiwe; babusisiwe abangabonanga\x + Luka 1.45.\x*\x + 1 Pet. 1.8. Mat. 13.16. 2 Kor. 5.7. Joha. 1.50.\x*, kanti bakholiwe\x + Luka 1.45.\x*.
\s Umsebenzi wevangeli
\p
\v 30 Njalo\x + 21.25.\x* uJesu wazenza lezinye izibonakaliso ezinengi phambi kwabafundi bakhe\x + 12.37. 4.48.\x*, ezingalotshwanga kulolugwalo.
\v 31 Kodwa lezi zilotshiwe, ukuze likholwe ukuthi uJesu unguKristu\x + Luka 1.4.\x* iNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 14.33.\x*, njalo ukuze lithi, likholwa, libe lempilo\x + 3.15,16. 5.24.\x* ebizweni lakhe\x + Seb. 3.6,16. 4.10. 1 Kor. 6.11.\x*.